  <p>Block 5 is location-choice day for the <a href="/units/unit-2/assessment-landscape-reading/">Landscape Reading</a> assessment. Students work through the 9 Chennai-area location cards (Cooum, Adyar, Marina, Pulicat, Mahabalipuram, Eastern Ghats, Buckingham Canal, Red Hills, AISC campus) and select one with reasoning. They then start annotating field photos using at least 5 vocabulary terms and pose two questions that the photos alone cannot answer.</p>
